spec_data.Name: python3-h5io
spec_data.Description:
h5io is a package designed to facilitate saving some standard Python objects
into the forward-compatible HDF5 format.
It is a higher-level package than h5py.

Python 3 version.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 01:22:17 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Read and write simple Python objects using HDF5
